{"type":"message","id":"d428b454","parentId":"e63e36c5","timestamp":"2026-03-04T11:26:19.821Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Outlining runtime store and UI components**\n\nI'm planning a runtime hook system using Zustand to simulate model data and manage prompt, activations, and patching state. I’ll build new components like PatchControlPanel, ScrubTimeline, and CircuitInspector to integrate with this store, refactor App.tsx to use it, and consider updating CSS for these additions. This setup should let me connect prompt control and activation matrix to a simulated runtime and display runtime metrics and controls neatly.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_044be20a9efe26f90169a816cd2bd081918414591149546f63\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpqBbbUexnkFsaOy6HXF1QHWCT8iAgrnvBm4_fmkRgtKpfyuRduBiv1WeLpNLHreb0L9MhscTgNC0xsLFO5nmqhfotinyJGYWVzklDkda7YVbQG8z52Ywv5v_5InIF3ZvPhCgYvatn_9nwQZdnkvUKCjtdIhSFndy8Sv-G2pfqXf9z_XHiHXvLa4ZGX_7f0sbwzqhdyyaUnxlV0BfrI93usbigFEPqLGyvKo6R8LFQwTeYyxQJxSD-R6EBs_-zpYT33a3fkIgdQnx7pd89kfBbP3e7_Hdq_nrYkcrqkcZsE_7PH7Q3dYwp8EfI4gCu61U-NXwPh8TPNZ17EQx_hQDdq-UNHLIpJg7a_GLwRDFIj-u3icdh8GLO1o0oqXt5Rjz5bJZVljdR2XX_XLAmLskt2lMMDMb6QjFj-oOwoVcUIZ96qnEamqfKRuUQaJK9EJzAZLb3BSHltARg8KSNO3bRMDvQpvS7D2UD08iHSynlcTYNu2CA0TkgDcpOjTfCv5lKpauT78LF9trPwUJOS26p-qNDWpt2h6UCH5SRNg8hvMdSsB4VacDL1Z4O1PAOi8X-34N6K8YmmYLHTcH5lEyD25S3kkAYluJI0Q0FdUudKn9-UuVLe48k7zvcdcrsxfCldltQ9XP8CEydQ7Wkazh06xdvVtXP7k_bevW6m-47EovQJ9WfbfGHmVFsajvi5kuD9ZIzY7wxawQMTr92lH_37HALR2pDJszFbcj2aoQHtDHSejAsbqzP_EK8SmFi6nxNSAqN2VIpNzUbAQ6fmBqXQW_0NY5tOXgzklugd3F_NMgWl0mUxY5wDTxicMF6_hwosqJrbz9a6SVZnLRBd3RYwmtrHjeP0T4XV5FlV_V34Ug7g6vU80CduTTV_JhyeoF3LD4bCTnl6XuT-Qw932fiTO5zipDUXqjlxd4gZ1PLl9oBYXorFwMrTDyo0ZzVms8qCojfdxkce2Ce6mTeFgUXfz8ThmUVyGfN6Chk_2KoigNtaJGM9wCebuBoFDKE29hFJ5tVluaSEMvFb9_vIcb9AFlAJRVnthRfwQ5XdYS_s40F-QZmQEjbOgUZMfoCCnoDRYj2r5c2bAQnbPEgMSeB9tUobg4EPP9P4kcPJyEj6xR5sF1D5t_89fiMXHXXHwOdWFAehiacvdDTG5F2VywNf7s3XSd4qoUS