{"type":"message","id":"6687c799","parentId":"d428b454","timestamp":"2026-03-04T11:26:19.845Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_xz5QTm0VYl0WUdsZUgJZlEAv|fc_044be20a9efe26f90169a816dbb90481918e2f38724a2ee7c7","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#root {\n  min-height: 100vh;\n  background: radial-gradient(circle at top, rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.2), transparent 45%), #f5f7fb;\n}\n\n.app-shell {\n  max-width: 1200px;\n  margin: 0 auto;\n  padding: 4rem 1.5rem 5rem;\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: column;\n  gap: 2rem;\n}\n\n.hero {\n  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.98);\n  border-radius: 20px;\n  padding: 3rem;\n  border: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);\n  box-shadow: 0 25px 45px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);\n}\n\n.hero h1 {\n  font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 4vw, 3.6rem);\n  margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem;\n  line-height: 1.2;\n}\n\n.hero-subtitle {\n  color: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.8);\n  max-width: 62ch;\n  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n}\n\n.eyebrow {\n  text-transform: uppercase;\n  letter-spacing: 0.3rem;\n  font-size: 0.85rem;\n  color: #6366f1;\n}\n\n.hero-actions {\n  display: flex;\n  gap: 1rem;\n  flex-wrap: wrap;\n}\n\nbutton {\n  border-radius: 999px;\n  padding: 0.85rem 1.6rem;\n  font-size: 1rem;\n  font-weight: 600;\n  border: none;\n  cursor: pointer;\n  transition: transform 150ms ease, box-shadow 150ms ease;\n}\n\nbutton.primary {\n  background: #6366f1;\n  color: white;\n  box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.25);\n}\n\nbutton.primary:hover {\n  transform: translateY(-1px);\n}\n\nbutton.ghost {\n  background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.08);\n  color: #1f2937;\n}\n\n.feature-grid {\n  display: grid;\n  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));\n  gap: 1rem;\n}\n\n.feature-card {\n  background: #ffffff;\n  border-radius: 16px;\n  padding: 1.75rem;\n  border: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);\n  box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.05);\n}\n\n.feature-card h3 {\n  margin-top: 0;\n  margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\n  font-size: 1.2rem;\n}\n\n.feature-card p {\n  margin: 0;\n  color: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.7);\n}\n\n.panel-grid {\n  display: grid;\n  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));\n  gap: 1rem;\n}\n\n.panel {\n  background: #0f172a;\n  color: white;\n  border-radius: 20px;\n  padding: 1.8rem;\n  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);\n}\n\n.panel-heading {\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: column;\n  gap: 0.5rem;\n  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n}\n\n.panel-heading span {\n  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\n  font-size: 0.85rem;\n}\n\n.activation-list {\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: column;\n  gap: 1rem;\n}\n\n.activation-row {\n  display: flex;\n  justify-content: space-between;\n  align-items: center;\n  border-radius: 12px;\n  padding: 1rem;\n  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);\n}\n\n.label {\n  font-weight: 600;\n  margin: 0;\n}\n\n.note {\n  margin: 0.25rem 0 0;\n  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\n  font-size: 0.85rem;\n}\n\n.value {\n  font-size: 1rem;\n  font-weight: 600;\n  color: #a5f3fc;\n}\n\n.graph-wrapper {\n  height: 320px;\n}\n\n.runtime-grid {\n  display: grid;\n  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));\n  gap: 1rem;\n}\n\n.runtime-card {\n  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);\n  border-radius: 16px;\n  padding: 1.5rem;\n  border: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.1);\n  box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);\n}\n\n.runtime-card h3 {\n  margin-top: 0;\n  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\n}\n\n.runtime-card p {\n  margin: 0;\n  color: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.7);\n}\n\n@media (max-width: 640px) {\n  .hero {\n    padding: 2.2rem;\n  }\n\n  .hero-actions {\n    flex-direction: column;\n  }\n}\n\n.prompt-panel {\n  background: #ffffff;\n  border-radius: 20px;\n  padding: 1.5rem;\n  border: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.07);\n  box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.06);\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: column;\n  gap: 0.75rem;\n}\n\n.prompt-panel__status {\n  margin: 0;\n  color: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.7);\n  font-size: 0.95rem;\n}\n\n.prompt-control {\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: column;\n  gap: 0.5rem;\n  border-radius: 14px;\n  padding: 1rem;\n  border: 1px solid rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.3);\n  background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.04);\n}\n\n.prompt-control__label {\n  font-size: 0.85rem;\n  text-transform: uppercase;\n  letter-spacing: 0.2rem;\n  color: #4c1d95;\n}\n\n.prompt-control__field {\n  display: flex;\n  gap: 0.5rem;\n}\n\n.prompt-control__input {\n  flex: 1;\n  border: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.15);\n  border-radius: 999px;\n  padding: 0.7rem 1.25rem;\n  font-size: 1rem;\n}\n\n.prompt-control__button {\n  border-radius: 999px;\n  padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;\n  border: none;\n  background: #4c1d95;\n  color: white;\n  font-weight: 600;\n  cursor: pointer;\n}\n\n.activations-panel__matrix {\n  margin-top: 1.5rem;\n}\n\n.activations-matrix {\n  border-radius: 16px;\n  overflow: hidden;\n  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: column;\n  gap: 0.4rem;\n  background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.15);\n}\n\n.activations-matrix__row {\n  display: flex;\n  justify-content: space-between;\n  align-items: center;\n  padding: 0.9rem 1rem;\n  border-radius: 12px;\n  background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.25);\n}\n\n.activations-matrix__row--negative {\n  background: rgba(244, 114, 182, 0.15);\n}\n\n.activations-matrix__row--positive {\n  background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.15);\n}\n\n.activations-matrix__neuron {\n  font-weight: 600;\n}\n\n.activations-matrix__impact {\n  font-weight: 700;\n  color: #fdfdfd;\n  min-width: 60px;\n  text-align: right;\n}\n\n.activations-matrix__note {\n  font-size: 0.85rem;\n  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772623579843}}
{"type":"message","id":"5923192a","parentId":"6687c799","timestamp":"2026-03-04T11:26:30.699Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Designing runtime store and components**\n\nI'm mapping out a sizable update to introduce a runtime model store using Zustand, defining new data structures for activations, circuits, patches, and scrub runs. I'll create several new components to display and control these data, update types for activation entries while avoiding circular dependencies, reorganize App.tsx to integrate everything, and add fresh CSS styles for the new sections. This will bring more interactive runtime insights and control into the app!","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_044be20a9efe26f90169a816dcdc7c8191915ef44e2415e620\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpqBbm9Xy8UJQMwfn_1oKP_bPe5utS6p2mOEzBmeuVBvolaLyFKnNjIrDYRTzGlHxSXfadtGGA9IayUHm0X4cbqML6DsIp0IV_u0a8dd0CTpnUirJ0_7hNpwJyTqGo0I5TqmkktQmLQ5SFDIch_2TO268qJHvCS4_2kY5ovWb3VNJ2Mnhj6PvCLIpbhKsA9jcO_BFb-CcYLyP5sEYzUCHKWrARJ3mfbHxV7ZVOCs7Cr8fop53UHsPVbahi6xi_6c_PChWWT02L-hEnZjkg1KQOzI8zAIWOy8_Hv9RKsLPKqNKNe89U60wMJVEfegsmGdS4onVzgh8ybwD3ZrkyAjd_bzn5lQ4_rDreyo8lP0YU5lax8V5S1ZyyYy69-IDtDDjRFwet5qWsdWjA6dJ48ffN7O42QkdwSw8wixrXkOniGL6aOwpkswCzp3oPfypKa6hrru2r4ZNSYi8Aoz4M4fQfAyU6dt1IOv858T9tJKO0_fGLHdo04t7ShtWl1VATL7RNpw0oiul0oWgqa0FwOPWVXF_HN_o9vXpLasAGvvj-c1zQzD7f9NcxfyRQfnxBIKTuO-5sDiZcHmR38GguA3e3VbGfSjaxba3AcVcwKrgUOA-J2ijvM6Yt1OajCDJQgdH7Y16oKPuX-6PyLP9BcoR0I1Ds8OszZZygpf9GY91osFBoDc8esFSqDutGqV5JIe2lcc3l75qg8GcItkvsG7s6P3oyoAFKeIWgXm_qZh4VuKb19rFGSL2hBaFn8LsKXkK01AdHG0ZUDhJsjx1UOrKVmShTY6LH96hDlyTkjj31mRKamkTS7Cdd6j5a4kZFP4PW2w3lLnFfdu1QMgpCDZXfbwP-wlSc2ofkbTqNMQHWYQ8P0QvjBxaI0jqwruNuJ5oMlMJ7-9xYsgZxImrrTk3c9V2H90VlBmItVjzZMV9upjK0c31TgQkOPuvHxLUL1rN9rN8QkmqnOu1MxUBV7RX8NjAdO3aHY9ad0XBMS14846LotXGqKGkCwsZe_U2nydIw3Zm51BHbUliS6yDwfP_-kjrfVD2-EK-emisPxDE5czCq1a0DIC3MgjBElg3pZ5yiz3hmszANtIFxUP6iXUvloxYguWZGZQNMqmezB3eJmZA5x3li76RwKUKOIh44yDqTcQrkj8uOMWDKgsDcH