{"type":"message","id":"93738250","parentId":"73dfa7f7","timestamp":"2026-03-04T11:26:52.970Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Building runtime state management**\n\nI'm laying out a Zustand store for managing model runtime data, defining types and base data for activations, nodes, and edges. I'll implement functions to randomize activations deterministically by hashing the prompt, handle patch application with summaries and impact shifts, and manage scrub runs with labels and logit shifts. State will also track node selection and update nodes' flow status based on prompt progress to support the CircuitInspector UI.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_044be20a9efe26f90169a816ebcbd08191a92660febb93fdcc\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpqBbyqwMNwkpjVy4ZND4WPFbtNZuhpAAjRce6bfSYBXF2ghEWsFc6f06-DJFaIIE949YYjEECtvgm-Q3682EJu4Un4lwnfrO1XG2AxFHPUdkA4olH6DrVYc5hYSEcQImREyGHipzfAkjomY3l_0LRsRxLbfL-vDv_eQDR5PCpW6hfQSPF9HoUVvDB1bGB--AoZQFnmm2jcjhp3_ICo3BzncclAgho7DJjW6V9ZeUCXNjFH0VI-WaHvNT_y5cpc2gd29OajGte1qkDgvQOznLmHuvIMkovXn5cugulgVgyf7vpC3iFTDZ7dPYKyOF3tolDfEHuBHnjWaVMkGz4QjmZItrP9_-VmUnz_9G3Yso1tkBkDpMnS7rf1Va1hT2MQb9Zb2s74U_iK9Uki3Nb62d2VkCQ2F1IFBOeXaxN8q4NWvbB_IpGBhWdgtzASiV047yAPEbczHsEvHxFtDnIqe3DXp6qD2UrQBPz5U9zifXm9vZsLbe8nHh4OQyYW7atcMaB3iZJmZ0ainJimdWVeX1cjWtwQy5Vw8wXv_NIvvmvQXcP4TJnTZWD6Jh9JliH-VHraf38dRScuZZBaml7K11INe6SAgctio8ioh0NcX8rjz8SYQTvY43HwJoplI3BMKpl6keo1np78-oGExRcRHfQiUh8vScj7x1ViOSjEH8SF-UT6U30XGfOFj7lE8J5Lra2cPJY2GZgZmwE9VeZzAY_fzevWj7XUbppfb6Y675y1EgNcmhnQN3zNwWZU8YGG3Jxgbr6ItBB-mcJeWAtj4lxCpywuQktnR-Ssk5F1IerIBCYF0r2BosqWdp6T9OK-T98qcbEY1dBhLRxAkisPQqgJebbb06jDxnHjUl8eCGk2aeT6uLFnhTWs0WScE51kqHfe4RP680kAp2nFnGAm886SkEse4V-xCytgut9YHkCZdCkRlKO8lFJ3HmSqOJEcb3z4qMGMCVb4s0ShLSJ9ePV_nbPHoe0SQgeKeb69FnMPyMpugMLu_UvrPUQVHPTQr8lXVUUd-iDaBwRf17suy2bxj8aH_PcKLJwNEUAP7UwyWWAIUtZBD-hljBUXVzMynixAxEABZ6xe92FG8ffMV9IzyWm60Rief60EW_Hie-8gkjiKmaVim1QaTFlAyyG15BbDFf1x8NVQVbeGx3JsrUeJbGRHgw18czFe8n7Gs1