ate (`isLoading`, `runtimeError`), the patch/scrub panels, circuit inspector, and runtime overview so every panel now reflects live model data (tokens parsed, patch summary, circuit node signals, scrub runs, and status messaging).\n- Added the new `transformerRunner` module, activation/scrub types, and refreshed CSS to style the runtime status/error banners plus the inspection grid around the new panels.\n\nTests:\n- `npm run test:unit`\n- `npm run build` *(reports the existing chunk-size warning: `transformers` + `onnxruntime-web` (~820 KB) triggers the default 500 KB warning; the runtime chunk is intentionally large because of the WebAssembly/QNN assets.)*","textSignature":"msg_044be20a9efe26f90169a81922ca6881919311fc56d4e690b5"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.1-codex-mini","usage":{"input":489,"output":663,"cacheRead":105600,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":106752,"cost":{"input":0.00012225,"output":0.001326,"cacheRead":0.0026400000000000004,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00408825}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772624155559}}
